commitResults.messageBody: Tag command can now add tags to existing tags.

Tag command now supports deleting tags instead of overriding.
Tag command can add and delete tags concurrently, which can be
multiple number of tags or none.
However, one field (either newTag or deleteTag) must be provided if the
other is not in use.
